{"tid":2267250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美國大選】被指擬初步點票佔優即宣布勝利 特朗普否認","createTime":"2020-11-02T02:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T02:55:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"337d020c908e448b885cc9926e9d43b04d2fc851","tid":2267250,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:53:15.000Z","msg":"....<br />\n特朗普說，不能在大選當晚就知道結果是非常差的安排，他的律師團隊當晚會監督點票，又暗示某些州份可能出現選舉舞弊：「我們不想等待賓夕凡尼亞州（點票），那兒有個政治州長，是黨派人物......我們不想見到的情況是他天天看著點票，看看是否還能找到多 1 萬張票。」<br />\n<br />\nAxios 報道，過去幾星期，特朗普曾私下跟官員談論大選當晚就要宣布自己勝選。他的團隊認為，要做到這步，特朗普要在俄亥俄州、佛羅里達州、北卡羅來納州、德州、愛荷華州、亞利桑那州和喬治亞州的初步點票中有壓倒性優勢。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，特朗普的顧問團隊近日似乎對選情更樂觀，他們稱關鍵州份的初步分析顯示，德州、內華達州、北卡羅來納州、亞利桑那州和威斯康星州的選情都比預期好，只有喬治亞州及愛荷華州是特別差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%93%AC%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8%E4%BD%94%E5%84%AA%E5%8D%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E4%25BD%2594%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6683ba2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E4%25BD%2594%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&h=bbbb5e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%93%AC%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8%E4%BD%94%E5%84%AA%E5%8D%B3%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D/</a>"},{"pid":"b2a16c3fa5c7548cebe0265a955f9aa7e473e658","tid":2267250,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"我登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b038e96d248ca996d3cf8b34bcbf004823244bb7","tid":2267250,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"登登登登登燈"}]}